data.description: Welcome to 135 Oconee Meadows! Nestled in the serene landscapes of Eatonton, Georgia, this charming property offers a perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and natural beauty. This delightful home features an open floor plan, fenced in back yard, and well maintained landscaping. With a great room offering a fireplace and large center island off the kitchen that is ideal for family gatherings and a space for relaxation and entertainment. Situated in the picturesque Oconee Meadows community with no HOA restrictions, residents here enjoy access to local shopping and dinning and lake access close by. Whether you're looking to unwind in nature or explore the vibrant local scene, this location offers something for everyone. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your home! Schedule a viewing today and experience the charm of 135 Oconee Meadows for yourself.
